.volcanic_apps
  .row
    .col-md-12
      %h3 The Eventbrite app allows you to import an event from your Eventbrite account to your website.
      %hr.featurette-divider
      %h4 Setup instructions 
      %p="1) Login to your Eventbrite account (this should be the account you use for creating the events you want to import to the website )." 
      %p="2) Then navigate to #{link_to 'http://www.eventbrite.com/myaccount/apps/new/', 'http://www.eventbrite.com/myaccount/apps/new/', target: '_balnk'} and fill out the form.".html_safe 
      %p="3) Make sure you enter the address of your website in the  Application URL  and OAuth Redirect URI fields and Submit the form"
      %p="4) On the following page click the 'Show Client Secret and OAuth Token' link. "
      %p="5) In section that is revealed locate the 'Your personal OAuth token' value and copy it into the field bellow (on this page) and click update"
      %br
      
      %p
